                <p>
                    <lb n="1"/>svastiśrīḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> tribhuvanakumāraveśyā bhujaṃga Arirājaveśyābhujaṃga Abhinava bhoja
                    <lb n="2"/>bhujabalarāma bhūpāla vidyādhara raṇaraṃgarākṣasa Uddaṇḍa pratā
                    <lb n="3" break="no"/>pa mānamarddana Āsavāra revanta śarīrasaṃpatyā sakara trirāyasā
                    <lb n="4" break="no"/>rdūla Ayyaṃgamalaparāyaragaṇḍa parameśvara padakamala paramārādha
                    <lb n="5" break="no"/><unclear>ka</unclear> gaṇḍagopāla śiraḥkantukakrīḍāvinoda rāyamīsaragaṇḍa
                    <lb n="6" break="no"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> darapāṇḍyaku<unclear>mā</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> 
                    <lb n="7"/>ra pāṇḍyastāpanā
                </p>
                
